Package controller

Class SearchController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.SearchController
  • public class SearchController
extends java.lang.Object
    The SearchController class is responsible for handling user interactions for the scene Search (Search.fxml). This scene occurs when the user clicks search within the UserAlbums scene.
    Author:
    Vincent Phung, William McFarland
